"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The European Union imposed new sanctions on Russia, targeting entities supporting Russia's war efforts. The EU also sanctioned businesses in India and China with ties to Russia. Meanwhile, Somalia agreed to let Turkey defend its waters to prevent threats from abroad.\",            \"english_title\": \"European Union Sanctions on Russia and Somalia-Turkey Deal\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Uni\u00f3n Europea impuso sanciones nuevas a Rusia, apuntando a entidades que apoyan los esfuerzos de guerra de Rusia. La UE tambi\u00e9n sancion\u00f3 negocios en India y China con v\u00ednculos a Rusia. Mientras tanto, Somalia acord\u00f3 dejar que Turqu\u00eda defienda sus aguas para prevenir amenazas del extranjero.\",            \"translated_title\": \"European Union Sanctions on Russia and Somalia-Turkey Deal\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Boeing replaced the head of the factory building 737 Max 9 jets after a recent incident. In South Africa, the finance minister announced plans to raise additional funds through taxes on goods and maintain tax brackets amid inflation.\",            \"english_title\": \"Boeing Leadership Change and South Africa's Budget Plans\",            \"translated_version\": \"Boeing reemplaz\u00f3 al jefe de la f\u00e1brica que construye los aviones 737 Max 9 despu\u00e9s de un incidente reciente. En Sud\u00e1frica, el ministro de finanzas anunci\u00f3 planes para recaudar fondos adicionales a trav\u00e9s de impuestos sobre bienes y mantener los niveles de impuestos en medio de la inflaci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Boeing Leadership Change and South Africa's Budget Plans\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Rio Tinto approved a $20bn mining project in Guinea, West Africa, expected to start iron ore deliveries next year. This project offers hope for the global mining industry.\",            \"english_title\": \"Rio Tinto's Mining Project in Guinea\",            \"translated_version\": \"Rio Tinto aprob\u00f3 un proyecto minero de $20 mil millones en Guinea, \u00c1frica Occidental, que se espera comience a entregar mineral de hierro el pr\u00f3ximo a\u00f1o. Este proyecto ofrece esperanza para la industria minera global.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Rio Tinto's Mining Project in Guinea\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A Ukrainian air strike reportedly killed over 65 Russian soldiers in occupied territory in eastern Ukraine. The strike followed the capture of a nearby town by Russian forces.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukrainian Air Strike in Eastern Ukraine\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ataque a\u00e9reo ucraniano supuestamente mat\u00f3 a m\u00e1s de 65 soldados rusos en territorio ocupado en el este de Ucrania. El ataque sigui\u00f3 a la captura de una ciudad cercana por fuerzas rusas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ukrainian Air Strike in Eastern Ukraine\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The European Space Agency predicted that the ERS-2 satellite launched in 1995 will re-enter the atmosphere and burn up on Wednesday. ERS-2 and its predecessor gathered valuable data on various environmental factors.\",            \"english_title\": \"European Space Agency's Satellite Re-Entry Prediction\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Agencia Espacial Europea predijo que el sat\u00e9lite ERS-2 lanzado en 1995 reingresar\u00e1 a la atm\u00f3sfera y se quemar\u00e1 el mi\u00e9rcoles. ERS-2 y su predecesor recopilaron datos valiosos sobre varios factores ambientales.\",            \"translated_title\": \"European Space Agency's Satellite Re-Entry Prediction\"        }    ]}"